long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Browser Plane is an AI-powered Chrome extension that acts as a copilot for every website you visit. It can see and understand the content of the webpage, allowing it to assist you with a wide range of tasks and boost your productivity.

Leverage the latest AI models, including GPT-4, Claude, and more, to get contextual help and insights for the website you're on.
